			<ns0:name>pdox%goo...@gtempaccount.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/104735739662288482898/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">I suggest allowing sequences of the form:

movslq %eax, %rax
movq disp(%r15,%rax,scale), %dest

(the base register could also be %rbp or %rsp)

The first instruction ensures that %rax is between -2^31 and 2^31 - 1.
This should be safe, as long as the lower guard region is at least 20 GB.
